## Frequently Asked Questions

**Can I get 0% down payment for commercial HP?**
It is possible for new equipment if your company has a very strong financial profile, or if the manufacturer is running a promotion. For used equipment, expect to pay at least 10-20% down.

**Does the OPR hike affect my existing HP loan?**
No. Since most HP loans are fixed-rate, your monthly installment remains the same even if Bank Negara raises the OPR.

**What is the maximum tenure for commercial machinery?**
Typically 3 to 7 years. Some specialized equipment might go up to 10 years, but 5 years is the "sweet spot" for most lenders.

**What happens if I can't pay for one month?**
Talk to your lender *before* you miss the payment. Most (especially non-bank lenders) are willing to work out a temporary solution if you are honest with them. If you just "disappear," repossession proceedings usually start after 2-3 months of arrears.

